rows.label: qst202317_0010
rows.name:
Hey... I don't know how this small fry
got a cool name like "Thanatobeast"...

rows.label: qst202317_0020
rows.name:
Hardly worthy of the name!
It fought like it didn't even care.

rows.label: qst202317_0030
rows.name: What... The little blighter's come back to life!

rows.label: qst202317_0040
rows.name:
It looks that way.
Incredible regenerative powers...

rows.label: qst202317_0060
rows.name:
So we went to all that trouble,
and now it's alive again?

rows.label: qst202317_0080
rows.name: But... What if monster just come back to life AGAIN?

rows.label: qst202317_0100
rows.name:
If it's not dead, well, I'll just
get to kill it all over again!

rows.label: qst202317_0110
rows.name: All right! Time for Round Two!
